          <div class="section_2"><h2><a name="Articles-Articles"></a>Articles</h2>

<ul>
	<li><span class="nobr"><a href="https://open-esb.dev.java.net/public/whitepapers/JBIforSOI.pdf">Using JBI for service oriented integration</a></span> by Ron Ten-Hove</li>
	<li><span class="nobr"><a href="http://www.fiveclouds.com/articles/2006/02/11/servicemix-deployments-in-eclipse">Great article</a></span> by Philip Dodds showing ServiceMix deployments being created in Eclipse</li>
	<li><span class="nobr"><a href="http://www.zapthink.com/report.html?id=ZAPFLASH-10272004">SOA Governance: Reengineering IT Governance</a></span> By Jason Bloomberg</li>
	<li><span class="nobr"><a href="http://www.theserverside.com/articles/article.tss?l=JBIforSOA">JBI - A Standard-based approach for SOA</a></span> by Meeraj Kinnumpurath</li>
	<li><span class="nobr"><a href="http://www.javaworld.com/javaworld/jw-12-2005/jw-1212-esb.html">ServiceMix as an enterprise service bus</a></span> by J. Jeffrey Hanson</li>
	<li><span class="nobr"><a href="http://www.itarchitect.co.uk/articles/display.asp?id=222">Plug into JBI with ServiceMix</a></span> by Sing Li</li>
	<li><span class="nobr"><a href="http://java.sys-con.com/read/117740.htm">SOA + EDA = ServiceMix</a></span></li>
	<li><span class="nobr"><a href="http://java.sun.com/integration/">Sun's JBI site</a></span></li>
	<li><span class="nobr"><a href="https://wiki.objectweb.org/celtix/Wiki.jsp?page=Research">Celix's ESB links</a></span></li>
	<li>Steve Vinoski's <span class="nobr"><a href="http://dsonline.computer.org/portal/site/dsonline/menuitem.9ed3d9924aeb0dcd82ccc6716bbe36ec/index.jsp?&amp;amp;amp;amp;pName=dso_level1&amp;amp;amp;amp;path=dsonline/0507&amp;amp;amp;amp;file=w4tow.xml&amp;amp;amp;amp;xsl=article.xsl&amp;amp;amp;amp;">JBI article</a></span></li>
